Class ProxyableDatasetProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.retention.profile.ConfigurableGlobDatasetFinder
      • gobblin.data.management.retention.profile.ProxyableDatasetProfile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DatasetsFinder

    public class ProxyableDatasetProfile
extends ConfigurableGlobDatasetFinder
    A wrapper of ConfigurableGlobDatasetFinder that looks for data.management.retention.dataset.Datasets with FileSystems CleanableDatasets with FileSystems proxied as the owner of each dataset.
